OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FAristocrat Constance Marten and her
OL,7,Fconvicted rapist partner were warned
OL,8,Fagainst disruptions in the dock as
OL,9,Fthey were being sentenced over the
OL,10,Fdeath of their newborn baby.
OL,12,FMarten, 38, and Mark Gordon, 51, were
OL,13,Ffound guilty of manslaughter, child
OL,14,Fcruelty, concealing the birth of a
OL,15,Fchild and perverting the course of
OL,16,Fjustice following two trials spanning
OL,17,Fsix months each.
