OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FOn Monday, Judge Mark Lucraft KC
OL,7,Frepeatedly warned the pair about
OL,8,F"disruption" in the dock as lawyers
OL,9,Fmitigated for the pair ahead of their
OL,10,FOld Bailey sentencing.
OL,12,FThe couple were seen talking to each
OL,13,Fother, gesturing and passing notes as
OL,14,Fthey sat flanked by dock officers.
OL,16,FJudge Lucraft told them that their
OL,17,Fbehaviour showed a "complete lack of
OL,18,Frespect" to the court.
