OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FIn her statement, Mrs de Selliers said
OL,7,Fshe was "horrified" at how her
OL,8,Fdaughter had been characterised during
OL,9,Fher trials, saying it did not reflect
OL,10,F"the daughter I remember".
OL,12,FShe stated: "What I do know is she
OL,13,Fshowed sheer determination when
OL,14,Ffighting for her children and her
OL,15,Fdaughter Victoria.
OL,17,F"It is my sincere hope that when
OL,18,Fconsidering her future, her courage
OL,19,Fand loyalty and deep sense of fairness
OL,20,Fare not overlooked."
