OL,6,FMitigating for Gordon, Philippa
OL,7,FMcAtasney KC said he suffered "a great
OL,8,Fdeal of upset and anxiety" when
OL,9,FVictoria's older siblings were taken
OL,10,Finto care before she was born.
OL,12,FShe told the court: "He says that the
OL,13,Fchildren being taken away affected
OL,14,Feverything, affected their whole
OL,15,Flives, and they were suffering a
OL,16,Ftrauma, and he accepts that poor
OL,17,Fdecisions were made which he very much
OL,18,Fregrets.
OL,20,F"He said he will live with this for
OL,21,Fthe remainder of his life."
