OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FPolice launched a nationwide hunt
OL,7,Fafter their car burst into flames on a
OL,8,Fmotorway near Bolton, Greater
OL,9,FManchester, on January 5 2023.
OL,11,FThe defendants travelled across
OL,12,FEngland and went off-grid, sleeping in
OL,13,Fa tent on the South Downs where baby
OL,14,FVictoria died days later.
OL,16,FAfter seven weeks on the run, the
OL,17,Fdefendants were arrested in Brighton.
OL,19,FAfter a desperate search, police found
OL,20,Ftheir baby dead amid rubbish inside a
OL,21,FLidl bag in a disused shed nearby.
