OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FVictoria's remains were too badly
OL,7,Fdecomposed to establish the cause of
OL,8,Fdeath.
OL,10,FThe prosecution said she had died from
OL,11,Fhypothermia in the cold and damp
OL,12,Fconditions inside the flimsy tent or
OL,13,Fwas smothered despite Marten being
OL,14,Fwarned by social workers about the
OL,15,Fdangers.
OL,17,FThe defendants claimed their
OL,18,Fdaughter's death was a tragic accident
OL,19,Fafter Marten fell asleep on her.
