OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FJurors in the first trial in 2024 were
OL,7,Fnot told about Gordon's violent past,
OL,8,Fwhich was only partly revealed in
OL,9,Ftheir second trial.
OL,11,FIn 1989, Gordon, then aged 14, held a
OL,12,Fwoman against her will in Florida for
OL,13,Fmore than four hours and raped her
OL,14,Fwhile armed with a knife and hedge
OL,15,Fclippers.
OL,17,FWithin a month, he entered another
OL,18,Fproperty and carried out another
OL,19,Foffence involving aggravated battery.
