OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FGordon, who moved with his mother from
OL,7,FBirmingham to the US at the age of 12,
OL,8,Fwas sentenced to 40 years in jail and
OL,9,Fwas released after 22 years.
OL,11,FIn 2017, Gordon was convicted of
OL,12,Fassaulting two female police officers
OL,13,Fat a maternity unit in Wales where
OL,14,FMarten gave birth to their first child
OL,15,Funder a fake identity.
OL,17,FJurors were not told that Gordon was
OL,18,Falso suspected of a incident of
OL,19,Fdomestic violence in 2019 which left
OL,20,FMarten with a shattered spleen.
