OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FGordon had refused to allow paramedics
OL,7,Finto their London flat to treat her
OL,8,Fafter she fell out of a window when
OL,9,Fshe was 14 weeks pregnant, it emerged
OL,10,Fduring legal argument.
OL,12,FShe spent eight days in hospital then
OL,13,Fput her life and that of her unborn
OL,14,Fchild at risk by attempting to
OL,15,Fdischarge herself, with Gordon's
OL,16,Fsupport, it was alleged.
OL,18,FIt was after that incident that the
OL,19,Ffamily court decided the couple's
OL,20,Fother children should be taken into
OL,21,Fcare.
