OL,3,CAristocrat and partner told off for
OL,4,C'disrupting' sentencing over baby death
OL,6,FWhen Marten became pregnant for a
OL,7,Ffifth time, she kept it secret, giving
OL,8,Fbirth in a hired holiday cottage on
OL,9,FChristmas Eve 2022.
OL,11,FThe defendants' attempts to keep
OL,12,FVictoria under wraps prompted the
OL,13,Fmajor police alert after a placenta
OL,14,Fwas found inside their abandoned car
OL,15,Fnear Bolton on January 5 2023.
OL,17,FWhile on the run, Victoria was only
OL,18,Fbriefly glimpsed on CCTV footage in
OL,19,FLondon wearing the same teddy bear
OL,20,Fmotif babygrow later recovered with
OL,21,Fher body inside the Lidl bag.
